<h2 id="govuk-paas">GOV.UK Notify</h2>

This platform makes it easy to keep your users updated. GOV.UK Notify makes it easy to create, customise and send:

- emails
- text messages
- letters

The platform can be used without the need for technical knowledge.

### Location

Amazon Web Services (AWS) UK data centres.

### Features

<a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.notifications.service.gov.uk/features">GOV.UK Notify features</a>

### Security

<a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.notifications.service.gov.uk/features/security">GOV.UK Notify security</a>

### Contract / MOU

DSS has established an Memorandum of Understanding (MOU) with the UK Cabinet Office to consume the service.

### Support

<a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.notifications.service.gov.uk/support">GOV.UK Notify support</a>

### Cost

Sending emails through this service is free. There is also a generous allowance of free text messages (250,000).

<a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.notifications.service.gov.uk/pricing">GOV.UK Notify pricing</a>

### Roadmap

<a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.notifications.service.gov.uk/features/roadmap">GOV.UK Notify roadmap</a>

### Predicted life span

The life span of this platform is not known. However, the platform is currently undergoing development and growth and features are being planned at least 2 years in advance.


